snippet.title: Vargverse is finally here!
snippet.description:
The wait is over! The time to enter the Vargverse is now!

The download link is here: https://brergrsartmugen.weebly.com/games.html

Individual downloads for characters (including MUGEN version 1.0 compatible versions) will be available soon!
